iated with defining $\\gamma_5$ in\ngeneric d dimensions. We show that leading contributions in the external\nmomenta can be reproduced by defining $\\gamma_5$ using the 't\nHooft-Veltman-Breitenlohner-Maison scheme.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 8 May 2020 17:43:52 GMT"}],"update_date":"2020-09-02"}
