 per day to other states of India was\nrecommended.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Sat, 9 May 2020 12:24:01 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Thu, 30 Jul 2020 18:01:12 GMT"}],"update_date":"2020-08-03"}
