red to\nunderstand to what extent this approach will provide improved diagnostic\nperformance, although it is logical to assume superior segmentation will lead\nto improved diagnostics.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Sat, 9 May 2020 12:32:25 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Sun, 12 Jul 2020 02:48:35 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Thu, 16 Jul 2020 03:33:03 GMT"}],"update_date":"2020-07-21"}
